{
  "stem": "1282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I mentioned to you, at home, we spoke Hungarian, so I spoke as fluently Hungarian as a native Budapest kid who's still not in the Army but is a Gentile kid.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I always had Gentile papers with me if I was stopped, OK?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unless if I was searched, that was a death sentence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if I was not searched and I showed them the Gentile papers, most of the time I got away with it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I was small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a small kid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- I knew the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I figured out the sewer system.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we had some engineers, some people that knew more than even I did, and they guided me, which sewer system, how I'll get into that building.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was more or less the delivery, the messenger who delivered these papers into these protected houses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were able to get them in a lot of times without papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then to get them out, there were always guards at the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was much harder to get them out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When you brought them in, they always thought, oh, let them be there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're-- they're behind the gate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We'll get them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But to get them out, they had to have something in their hands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was our job, or this is my job to get it to them so they can get out and then hand it over to a different group.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And each group didn't always know what the other group is doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We just had specific assignment without knowing too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If we knew too much, under torture we may have given away too much information and I may have condemned somebody.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I didn't want to-- need to know more than what my job was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beyond fear.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
